 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">然而，<span class="_ _7"></span>只要以佛法的智慧深入观察，<span class="_ _7"></span>最终就会明白，<span class="_ _7"></span>自己执</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya6 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">著的一切，<span class="_ _10"></span>名声、<span class="_ _a"></span>财产、<span class="_ _10"></span>地位、<span class="_ _10"></span>感情，<span class="_ _1f"></span>确确实实都是一场梦。<span class="_ _b"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x1b h4 ya7 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">有了佛法的智慧，<span class="_ _9"></span>即便不谈获得解脱，<span class="_ _9"></span>对现实生活也很</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya8 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">有用。<span class="_ _7"></span>以诸法如梦来说，<span class="_ _7"></span>如果我们经常思维：<span class="_ _7"></span>二十年前的一</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya9 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">切，<span class="_ _7"></span>跟二十年前的梦有什么区别；<span class="_ _7"></span>昨天发生的一切，<span class="_ _7"></span>跟昨晚</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yce ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的梦有什么区别……时间长了，就能减轻执著、消除烦恼。<span class="_ _a"></span> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
